query:
INSERT INTO job_queue (relative_path, user_id, job_type, priority)
        SELECT $1, $2, 'ANALYSIS', $3
        WHERE NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM queue_failures WHERE relative_path = $1 AND job_type = 'ANALYSIS'
        )
        ON CONFLICT (relative_path, job_type) DO UPDATE
        SET
            priority = $3,
            retry_count = 0,
            created_at = NOW()
